CR Legal Compliance Assessment Instance Record	CR Legal Compliance Assessment Instance Record	Legal Compliance Assessment Instance Record	##			The working materials and result of a legal support and assessment action	IO	IO		IO	O
			Legal Assessment Type 			The type of law that is applied by the assessment action	IO	IO		IO	O
			Business Unit Reference			The business function or unit assessed if appropriate	I	IO		IO	O
			Product/Service Reference 			The associated product/service being assessed if appropriate	I	IO		IO	O
			Customer Reference			Reference to the customer assessed if appropriate	I	IO		IO	O
			Jurisdiction Reference			Indication of the legal jurisdiction that applies	I	IO		IO	O
			Law Reference			Reference to the specific law	I	IO		IO	O
			Law Definition			A definition of the required behavior to remain within the law	O				O
			Law Compliance and Reporting Requirements 			Description of the measurements and reporting required to demonstrate legal compliance	O				O
			Law Compliance Accountability 			Explanation of the business context, responsibility and accountability for legal compliance	O				O
			Legal Penalties			Outline of the possible implications of breaking the law	O				O
			Legal Guideline			Guidelines and requirements for following the law	O				O
			Document Reference 			Reference to any documentation classified/archived as appropriate	IO	IO		IO	O
			Legal Assessment Work Products			Work documentation, forms and schedules produced and referenced during the legal assessment action	IO	IO		IO	O
			Legal Assessment Result			Outcome/result of the legal assessment, this can include remedial actions	O			O	O
